{"tid":279584,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇恒大精算?","createTime":"2017-06-11T11:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T13:50:25.000Z","uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8815d82531e05221655e72396d36bed5dc103709","tid":279584,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hsmc.edu.hk/en/academic-programmes/undergraduate/ain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsmc.edu.hk%2Fen%2Facademic-programmes%2Fundergraduate%2Fain&d=X%2BSTMYEMSAHrUNu%2FG3a63whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=22020656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hsmc.edu.hk/en/academic-programmes/undergraduate/ain</a><br />\n<br />\nachelor of Science (Honours) in Actuarial Studies and Insurance programme (the Programme) is designed to train professionals which are of keen demand by the insurance industry. The insurance industry in Hong Kong is experiencing a rapid growth and in need of a continuous supply of talents. The education on insurance professions cannot catch up with the fast development of the local economy. <strong>There is a lack of opportunities for young people to understand the career path of various insurance specialities.</strong> As a result, the newcomers fall short in meeting the strong demand of human resources in the market. Our goal is to offer a platform to connect the students and the industry. The Programme provides professional training on actuarial studies and insurance practice to students, helps them prepare for their future career; meanwhile, brings in new blood to the industry and fulfill the market needs.<br />\n<br />\n乞食之選? 未來保險業uw/claims/etc.打雜嘅&ldquo;main supplier&rdquo;?"},{"pid":"6a1b881de40daab83c4dfc7ccf5b9b19f1d5acc0","tid":279584,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hsmc.edu.hk/en/academic-programmes/undergraduate/ain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.